Prioritise ruthlessly.
Process ‚â† progress
We are a sports team and everyone plays a crucial role. Don't ever drop the baton. Will hurt the entire team.
Practice predicting the second and third order effects of your decisions.
Speed > perfection
Dream big. At https://t.co/x8lD1wYokn, we strongly believe we are building a multi unicorn. Remember, nothing big ever comes easy. Work hard. Enjoy the ride.
Feedback moves teams forward and helps you grow. Don't get offended or take it personally. When giving feedback, focus on 'delta' points. The 20% than can impact the 80%.
Don't take your ideas too seriously. Test everything. Move on quickly.
Innovation is our best friend. Getting attached to a process, our worst enemy. Everything that we do today can be improved.
When in doubt, let first principles guide you. For us it's to make our members win. If it helps our mission (more women in leadership positions), do it.
